{"tid":1748433,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日行出票站之後仲有一件事要做","createTime":"2019-11-23T16:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:00:29.000Z","uid":112094,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a639069c32919a75f3e8f1eab71406e3e70a4de","tid":1748433,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我入去抄number</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/dc19count\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fdc19count&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e516cabb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/dc19count</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">愈多人填愈準確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mdr3xXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdr3xXQ.jpg&h=a1d66496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 去票站門口揾「每小時的投票人數紀錄」(P15表格)<br />\n2. 撳入呢條link <a href=\"http://bit.ly/dc19count\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fdc19count&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e516cabb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/dc19count</a><br />\n3. 選擇地區同票站<br />\n4. 將「累積投票人數」（右手邊Column）入哂落張form度，無就漏空<br />\n每個小選區投票率會喺 <a href=\"http://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=a330046d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">vote4.hk</a> 同 選區事實處 <a href=\"http://hkfactcheck.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=cb9b782e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkfactcheck.io</a>  實時更新<br />\n<br />\n選區事實處<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/pollstat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fpollstat&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=78380693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/pollstat</a><br />\n<br />\n投票指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=669b957e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEiA812.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEiA812.png&h=5cf970cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 同傳真社有乜分別? <br />\nA: 傳真社係影相收集總結果作佢哋嘅調查報告，呢個係每一個時段填form收集+ 即時更新，<a href=\"http://上vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%8Avote4.hk&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=bd6a48e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">上vote4.hk</a> 或者 <a href=\"http://hkfactcheck.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2Fp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=cb9b782e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkfactcheck.io</a> 網站就有得睇即時投票率!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXGGjCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXGGjCH.jpg&h=96a1da06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e176cca48f96f628d40a6e2f60ad9c2e89290f","tid":1748433,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"住得近票站既人可以影低全日有幾多人入過票站，再交俾傳真社。<br />\n但唔好係禁區範圍影。"},{"pid":"868ba005a3ea203ab86317cc4ed14a4afb04a160","tid":1748433,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n一文分析區選及投票<br />\n<a href=